name: Corneo's Brigitte (Overwatch) Embedding
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding for Brigitte (Lindholm) from Overwatch.

Use corneo_brigitte to activate. The eyes are pretty bad in the embedding by itself, so you'll definitely want to prompt for the eyes to be a bit better, or just inpaint them after generating the rest of the image. I don't think this one works quite as well as my other character embeddings but it was a request so here it is! Also the training data may have gone a bit too hard on the muscular female approach, so unless you like your ladies with a LOT of muscles, you probably want to put (muscular:0.6) or thereabouts in your negative prompt.

Example images produced with OrangeCocoa available here https://civitai.com/models/4355/orangecocoa-5050-mix

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!
